{{question-answer|question=35. <math> \sqrt{x^2y^4} </math>|answer=<math>\mathbf{ xy^2 }</math>}}

{{question-answer|question=36. <math> \bigg(\frac{8x^6}{y^4}\bigg)^{1/3} </math>|answer=<math>\mathbf{ \frac{2x^2}{y^{\frac{4}{3}}}} </math>}}

