The '''rambutan''' is a tropical fruit from [[Cookbook:Cuisine of Thailand|Thailand]] and [[Cookbook:Cuisine of Malaysia|Malaysia]].

It is closely related to several other edible tropical fruits including the [[Cookbook:Lychee|lychee]], longan, and mamoncillo

