{{Calculus/Top Nav|Integration techniques/Numerical Approximations|Area}}

==Integration of Polynomials==
Evaluate the following:
{{question-answer|question=1. <math>\int (x^2-2)^{2}\, dx</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>\frac{x^{5}}{5}-\frac{4x^{3}}{3}+4x+C</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=2. <math>\int 8x^3\, dx</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>2x^{4}+C</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=3. <math>\int (4x^2+11x^3)\, dx</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>\frac{4x^{3}}{3}+\frac{11x^{4}}{4}+C</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=4. <math>\int (31x^{32}+4x^3-9x^4) \,dx</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>\frac{31x^{33}}{33}+x^{4}-\frac{9x^{5}}{5}+C</math>}}}}
{{question-answer|question=5. <math>\int 5x^{-2}\, dx</math>|answer={{noprint|<math>-\frac{5}{x}+C</math>}}}}
